# Arrowz - Aider AI Rules

## Project Information
- App: Arrowz - Enterprise VoIP & Omni-Channel Communications
- Framework: Frappe v15+
- Languages: Python 3.10+, JavaScript ES6+
- Database: MariaDB via Frappe ORM

## Important Directories
- API endpoints: arrowz/api/
- DocTypes: arrowz/arrowz/doctype/
- Integrations: arrowz/integrations/
- Frontend JS: arrowz/public/js/
- Frontend CSS: arrowz/public/css/

## Code Patterns

### Python API Pattern
```python
@frappe.whitelist()
def function_name(param: str) -> dict:
    """Docstring."""
    frappe.only_for(["Role"])
    return {"status": "success"}
```

### JavaScript Pattern
```javascript
arrowz.module = {
    init() { ... },
    async callApi() {
        const { message } = await frappe.call({
            method: 'arrowz.api.module.function'
        });
    }
};
```

### Real-time Events
```python
# Server
frappe.publish_realtime("event_name", data, user=user)
```
```javascript
// Client
frappe.realtime.on("event_name", (data) => { ... });
```

## Key Files
- hooks.py: App configuration
- tasks.py: Background jobs
- boot.py: Session data
- softphone_v2.js: WebRTC softphone
- omni_panel.js: Chat UI

## Naming Conventions
- DocTypes: AZ <Name> (e.g., AZ Call Log)
- Python: snake_case
- JavaScript: camelCase in arrowz.* namespace
- CSS: arrowz-* prefix

## Testing Commands
```bash
bench --site dev.localhost run-tests --app arrowz
bench build --app arrowz
bench --site dev.localhost clear-cache
```

## Context Files
- CONTEXT.md: Full technical context
- INTEGRATIONS.md: External systems
- AI_GUIDELINES.md: Coding guidelines
- ARCHITECTURE.md: System diagrams
